=Introduction=

The Performance viewpoint enables to simply describe the non-functional aspect of performance in Capella.
It provides several capabilities:

* Definition of performance value to be associated with model elements
* Definition of maximum performance value to be associated with model elements
* Computation of model element performance value based on self performance value and child performance values
* Visualization of maximum performance value compliance with regards to computed value